title: Week 15 preview & Rams vs Seahawks recap
itunes:title: Week 15 preview & Rams vs Seahawks recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Colleen Wolfe – go game-by-game previewing each week 15 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, NFL Network’s Gregg Rosenthal joins us from Seattle to recap the Thursday night game between the Rams and the Seahawks.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
